$ git branch -a
$ git remote -v
$ git branch
search the branch
$ git branch <name>
create the branch name
$ git checkout <name>
switch the branch name
$ git checkout -b <name>
create and switch that branch name
$ git merge <name>
merge the name branch to current branch
$ git branch -d <name>
del the name branch
$ git log --graph
show the log by graph
